
                        Section 4 - Notes
                     Pull Image Hello Service
                             
$ cd pullimage

# modify this file for busybox
$ cat docker-compose.yaml 
version: '3'
services:
  hello:
    image: busybox
    command: [/bin/echo, 'Hello from busybox!']

$ docker-compose up
Pulling hello (busybox:latest)...
